A promotional banner offers "25% off Large Meals on orders $25+ at HJs" with a code and an expiration date. At the bottom, there's a section for "Grocery essentials" from Coles, featuring images of milk and bananas, along with a delivery time estimate of 42 minutes. The navigation bar includes icons for Home, Grocery, Retail, Browse, and Orders.

flow_desc: To log out of the delivery service app, start by tapping on the profile icon located at the top of the app interface. This directs you to the account settings page, where you can manage various aspects of your profile. Next, tap on the profile title text to access your account information. Here, you'll find your personal details, including your name and email. Scroll to the bottom and tap on the "Log Out" button. A confirmation prompt will appear asking if you're sure about logging out. Confirm by tapping the "Log Out" button again to successfully complete the process.
